The course covers how to set up advertisements in various social media environments (Facebook, Instagram, Google). Students will learn how to create a comprehensive social media campaign, what a call-to-action is, and how Facebook Pixel helps in targeting warm audiences with advertisements.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to provide practical knowledge for creating advertisements on social media channels (Facebook, Instagram, Google). Additionally, learners will gain knowledge on creating organic content in these channels, including the type and format of the content.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) understands how to set up advertisements on Facebook, Instagram and Google; 2) comprehend the possibilities of implementing different platforms in their company's social media marketing;  3) grasp the principles of social media marketing and apply them in their work; 4) utilises social media platforms as marketing tools, organise various campaigns, and create quality content on appropriate channels.
